38:21.842 --> 38:23.636
Would you mind giving Marisol
a message from me?

38:24.285 --> 38:25.638
Okay.

38:25.679 --> 38:28.599
Ask her when's the last time she prayed?

38:28.641 --> 38:29.975
Can you remember that?

38:30.017 --> 38:32.019
I'm sorry. Who is this?

38:32.061 --> 38:33.896
Hello?

38:35.898 --> 38:38.067
Hey.

38:38.633 --> 38:40.194
Do we have any new numbers yet?

38:40.236 --> 38:43.072
Everyone has you winning
the debate by a landslide.

38:43.113 --> 38:44.949
Instant polls already have you up by ten.

38:44.990 --> 38:46.450
Fantastic.

38:46.891 --> 38:48.285
I'm exhausted.

38:48.327 --> 38:49.995
Who's Gabriel?

38:54.023 --> 38:55.626
Uh...

38:55.668 --> 38:57.628
He wanted me to give you a message.

38:57.670 --> 39:00.089
Uh, "When's the last time you prayed?"

39:01.239 --> 39:03.133
What does that mean?

39:08.413 --> 39:10.832
You ask a lot of questions, Elena.

39:11.875 --> 39:14.103
I'm just trying to keep you safe.

39:14.627 --> 39:16.522
You're very good at your job,

39:16.564 --> 39:19.233
but I think it's time for you to move on.

39:21.551 --> 39:23.028
You're firing me?

39:23.070 --> 39:24.822
No. Never.

39:24.864 --> 39:28.075
I'm giving you the freedom
to explore a new opportunity.

39:31.186 --> 39:34.248
Elena, the campaign is over.

39:35.190 --> 39:36.917
Senator Briggs from your hometown

39:36.959 --> 39:40.348
inquired about your service
a while ago, but at the time,

39:40.389 --> 39:41.630
I didn't want to let you go

39:41.672 --> 39:44.633
because you're such a valuable asset.

39:44.675 --> 39:48.178
But he's very impressed with
what you've done for me so far.

39:48.220 --> 39:50.955
I don't want to go back to Sacramento.

39:52.457 --> 39:57.187
I'm calling him and giving you
my highest recommendations.

39:57.229 --> 40:00.149
This is best for both of us.

40:02.750 --> 40:03.922
Good luck.

40:09.617 --> 40:11.827
I wish you the best.

40:16.815 --> 40:19.126
Anyways, Marisol's
really brave, you know?

40:19.168 --> 40:21.462
I mean, this guy came in today
who had a hook for a hand.

40:21.503 --> 40:22.755
No shit.

40:22.796 --> 40:24.757
- Yeah, it's crazy, right?
- Yeah.

40:24.798 --> 40:26.175
It was pretty weird.

40:26.658 --> 40:28.886
Marisol just walked right up to him

40:29.619 --> 40:31.388
and told him he needed
to make an appointment,

40:31.430 --> 40:34.892
but he kept insisting
and being really pushy with her

40:34.934 --> 40:36.894
and she stood her ground, though.

40:36.936 --> 40:38.086
Sent him on his way.

40:39.963 --> 40:42.691
Did you ever find out
what he wanted or who he was?

40:42.733 --> 40:45.464
- Uh-uh.
- Like a street person or something?

40:45.505 --> 40:48.364
- He said he was a disabled veteran.
- Oh.

40:48.405 --> 40:50.991
Those guys go through
a lot of shit, you know.

40:51.033 --> 40:55.162
He could've had... you know,
some kind of PTSD or whatever.

40:55.870 --> 40:57.913
Marisol was brave, though.

40:59.732 --> 41:01.168
If it were me, I probably would have

41:01.210 --> 41:02.544
just hidden in my office.

41:03.862 --> 41:05.714
I really like her.

41:05.756 --> 41:07.407
You do?

41:08.575 --> 41:10.469
- I think you made that clear.
- Mm-hmm.

41:10.511 --> 41:12.638
- About 300 times.
- Okay.

41:13.538 --> 41:15.557
You just seem really happy is all.

41:18.668 --> 41:20.270
I'm all right, I guess.

41:32.116 --> 41:33.742
Thank you, Luis.

41:33.784 --> 41:36.453
Of course, Ms. Silva, any time.

41:37.061 --> 41:38.706
Did Mr. McBride tell you?

41:38.747 --> 41:41.750
Yes. They're dropping the charges.

41:42.150 --> 41:45.671
I'm so happy.

41:45.987 --> 41:49.216
My girlfriend's gonna throw
this really big party.

41:49.782 --> 41:51.260
And I'd really like you to come.

41:51.301 --> 41:53.262
Of course, of course.

41:53.303 --> 41:54.746
I'll be there.

42:03.087 --> 42:05.423
You didn't deserve any...

42:07.091 --> 42:09.302
you didn't deserve any of this.

42:10.553 --> 42:13.323
Well, it's all going to be over soon.

42:15.743 --> 42:20.581
Look, thank you so much
for believing in me.

42:22.982 --> 42:24.752
I'll never forget it.

42:28.655 --> 42:30.758
I love you.

42:30.799 --> 42:32.968
I love you, too.

43:20.856 --> 43:21.999
Okay, Keith.

43:22.792 --> 43:24.144
Tell me.

43:24.186 --> 43:25.562
I can't.

43:25.604 --> 43:26.897
You owe me an explanation.

43:26.939 --> 43:28.357
I-I don't want you to get involved.

43:28.398 --> 43:30.567
Oh, yeah? I am fucking involved.

43:30.609 --> 43:32.152
We're all fucking involved.

43:32.194 --> 43:36.698
Look, all I can say is,
Danny came to me...

43:36.740 --> 43:38.450
- Yeah?
- ...with this thing.

43:38.492 --> 43:39.743
- What thing?
- Okay?

43:39.785 --> 43:41.703
- And-and-and it got out of hand.
- What?

43:41.745 --> 43:44.414
Do not touch me!

43:47.900 --> 43:50.337
- I could kill him.
- No.

43:50.379 --> 43:51.713
Where is he? I'll kill him.

43:51.755 --> 43:53.423
I need to own it.

43:58.053 --> 44:01.765
I did not sign up for this, Keith.

44:02.331 --> 44:04.309
I don't deserve this.

44:04.351 --> 44:06.228
Your kids don't deserve this.

44:06.270 --> 44:08.272
I know.

44:35.073 --> 44:37.509
What's gonna happen to Danny?

44:54.943 --> 44:56.945
Danny?

44:58.488 --> 45:00.449
It's him.

45:00.490 --> 45:02.451
It's fucking him.

45:02.492 --> 45:04.685
Well, Danny, you better take care of it.

45:07.021 --> 45:08.749
Wait, what?

45:08.790 --> 45:10.292
He's my-my fucking best friend, man.

45:10.334 --> 45:11.710
What are you talking about?

45:11.752 --> 45:13.945
And I'm very sorry about that.

45:15.446 --> 45:17.507
No, Tom, no...

45:24.330 --> 45:26.516
Fuck. Fuck!

46:29.020 --> 46:30.914
I have a surprise for you.

46:30.956 --> 46:32.582
I don't like surprises.

46:32.624 --> 46:36.336
I don't like them either, but...

46:36.777 --> 46:37.963
this is a good one.

46:38.005 --> 46:39.256
Yeah?

46:39.298 --> 46:40.674
Okay.

46:41.248 --> 46:42.700
What you got?

46:46.221 --> 46:48.497
I want you to come away with me.

46:51.459 --> 46:52.835
What do you mean?

46:53.895 --> 46:55.504
Right now.

46:58.341 --> 47:00.527
You're not too busy running for mayor?

47:00.569 --> 47:02.446
Just one night, and, you know,

47:02.487 --> 47:04.156
my numbers are up.

47:04.639 --> 47:07.034
I think it would be good
just to get away from all this.

47:07.075 --> 47:08.517
Yeah.

47:09.786 --> 47:11.496
Sounds good to me.

47:11.538 --> 47:13.707
- Good.
- Yeah.

47:13.749 --> 47:15.417
So, where-where are we going?

47:16.108 --> 47:18.295
Really? It's a surprise.

47:18.819 --> 47:20.589
Okay.

47:20.630 --> 47:21.965
I'm intrigued.

47:22.007 --> 47:24.301
Good.

47:24.343 --> 47:25.510
I think it's gonna be good.

47:26.535 --> 47:28.221
Would you go to the beach?

47:28.579 --> 47:29.997
Right now.

47:31.165 --> 47:32.625
Well...

47:33.643 --> 47:35.937
just go stand on the beach
and wait for you?

47:35.979 --> 47:37.129
Yes.

47:39.274 --> 47:41.985
Okay. You're gonna leave
and go home, aren't you?

47:44.178 --> 47:46.323
Well, should I just leave a credit card,

47:46.365 --> 47:48.408
- and they can bring...?
- No, everything's taken care of.

47:48.450 --> 47:50.786
- Really?
- Of course.

47:50.827 --> 47:52.329
No shit.

47:52.371 --> 47:53.985
I'll see you in a little bit.

47:54.010 --> 47:55.172
Yeah.

48:30.700 --> 48:32.643
Billy.

